Nothing Personal #1

MILEX, Minsk, Belarus 
05/2017

Edition 1/1

Nothing Personal - The Back Office of War (2016 - 2021)

Every day on the news we are watching pictures of war and destruction, and the expenditure on armaments is setting new records year after year. Nothing Personal shows the back office of war, which is the complete opposite of a battlefield: an oversized playground for adults with wine, finger food, and shiny weapons.

World Press Photo 2020 Winner
Leica Oskar Barnack 2021 Finalist
Miami Street Photo 2019 Winner
PH Museum Grant 2019 Winner

The series has been published and exhibited worldwide.
